Also Download Metadata table for Attribute Definition: http://gis.drcog.org/datacatalog/node/280 The Denver-Aurora-Boulder Combined Statistical Area Includes the entire DRCOG Region in addition to Park, Elbert, and all of Weld County.    The 2010 Census data by Block Groups can be linked using the geoid field, to the GEOID10 field in the BG_2010 Dataset: http://gis.drcog.org/datacatalog/content/block-groups-census-2010  NOTE:  When importing the .csv files into a Database,  the software may try to turn the geoid field into a number field, which will drop the first 0 from the census code and will make the table not linkable to the geographies.
